{"tid":1930294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃任匡：多咗人出街、少咗人帶口罩係兇兆；香港同意大利既距離，冇大家想像中咁遠","createTime":"2020-03-17T12:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T11:56:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f838ec06ff1ae9e12a0652eb2ba63315644bda6","tid":1930294,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"第二波來襲。<br />\n<br />\n但是，近日普遍戴口罩的人數卻似乎開始減少（相反見到冥頑不靈的鬼佬終於肯戴口罩），而街頭的人流開始回升。這實在是很危險的凶兆。<br />\n<br />\n香港人至今是做得很好沒錯，可是我們實在沒有自滿的本錢。因為香港和意大利，其實只是一線之差。<br />\n<br />\n一旦香港出現大型社區爆發，患者大幅上升，醫療資源耗盡的話，我們被迫像意大利的醫院一樣「揀人醫」，結果死傷枕藉，黑箱車日日來回醫院和殯儀館，並非天荒夜談。<br />\n<br />\n記著，就算沒有武漢肺炎，由於多年缺乏長遠醫療規劃，亦沒有制定人口政策，香港的醫療系統都已經瀕臨崩潰 &mdash; 我們本來就沒有甚麼餘裕了。<br />\n<br />\n只是，因為香港人過去三個月都很努力地保護自己，大大減輕了醫院的負荷，所以至今未全面爆煲，僅此而已（但其實在大家看不見的地方已經在爆了）。<br />\n<br />\n香港和意大利的距離，沒大家想像得那麼遙遠。<br />\n<br />\n所以還請大家切莫鬆懈：<br />\n戴口罩，勤潔手，<br />\n保持安全距離，<br />\n暫時避免外遊。<br />\n<br />\n祝各位廢青，肺清。<br />\n<br />\n作者facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%87%B6%E5%85%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2587%25B6%25E5%2585%2586%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzByZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=9c6a0685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2587%25B6%25E5%2585%2586%2F&h=de8a4ebd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%87%B6%E5%85%86/</a>"},{"pid":"c1cf1e44bfa1f04760611d2a49068edfe380dd1e","tid":1930294,"uid":126382,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"算啦，其實爆就爆硬，勸唔到，香港人個個都係你愈叫愈做，完全anti-social <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c03764277f97c2e62fb206d2ebb4d0a32e924b","tid":1930294,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"大家要保持警剔"},{"pid":"f64fd99f9e54e1cb5926ab7183f3a48e4ba4296b","tid":1930294,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"是但啦，全球攬炒"},{"pid":"22626625cad9e17734c589ae5d3f5cec4301b089","tid":1930294,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"攬炒呀，你驚？"},{"pid":"9fda83cb14afdfdc82cd18811322f6d483d91eab","tid":1930294,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"藍絲：相信政府"},{"pid":"0387ddd445c06399552d6e11b9bc73e2b9030dc8","tid":1930294,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb60aa8022e3ffc2cb835e8394178ef867c81856","tid":1930294,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"推 好多仆街老細復曬工 搵員工條命去博"},{"pid":"3f22ed1916822899fd2504f34041109551eb236f","tid":1930294,"uid":78470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"爆咪好囉 講左攬炒咁耐都未炒<br />\n啲港豬明知道有病毒仲去行山打卡就知講咁多無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10398f0abd26de2058768aa2ee680cef04a4ffc5","tid":1930294,"uid":275588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔復工咪少左人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放工地鐵都爆晒人"},{"pid":"1a4559d22c07c9c7c254f1c7df25a3ec70380fbb","tid":1930294,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"的確係多咗好多人出街<br />\n我除咗返工，每次出街都要諗過度過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2b54025fd1dd293ae16dc2663cfd1c251cb5a1","tid":1930294,"uid":180293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"香港根本隨時隨地都係全世界最危險既地方<br />\n4月一放返支那人落黎都時唔方唔爆過意粉"},{"pid":"ab2b1d92e9cc871356b3c1ec88624b6046a02acc","tid":1930294,"uid":1643,"like"